    "glyph": "MTC",
    "body": "Watch the webinar here if you’ve missed it.\n\n\n[▶ Watch the video on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFWt_-NaF8s)\n\n\nSteelTrace is hosting another webinar, this time we touch on the topic of Counterfeiting in the Steel industry.\n\n\nTogether with our guests [Fergus Mason](https://www.linkedin.com/in/fergus-mason-9a9566136/), Linepipe Manager – Middle East at [Marubeni Itochu](https://www.benichu.com/en/) Steel Inc and [Mark Walsh CQP MCQI](https://www.linkedin.com/in/mark-walsh-cqp-mcqi-b09760b/) Technical Director of [Q-Sys Solutions](https://qsys-solutions.com/) we will touch upon the various topics surrounding counterfeit material and its consequences.\n\n\nYou might also like to read our blog post [5 ways to find out if an MTC is fake](post.html?slug=5-ways-to-find-out-if-an-mtc-material-test-certificate-is-fake) where give 5 tips for quality managers on how to spot a fake certificate.",
    "summary": "SteelTrace is hosting another webinar, this time we touch on the topic of Counterfeiting in the Steel industry. Together with our guests Fergus Mason, Linepipe Manager - Middle East at Marubeni Itochu Steel Inc and Mark Walsh CQP MCQI Technical Director of Q-Sys Solutions we will touch upon the various topics surrounding counterfeit material and its consequences.",
